#2. Flexbox
display:flex;

Creates a flexible container.

By default children become

A B C

instead of

A
B
C

#3. justify-content

Controls horizontal alignment.

Example

justify-content:center;

Moves items to the center horizontally.

#4. align-items

Controls vertical alignment.

Example

align-items:center;

Moves items to the center vertically.

#5. gap

Instead of

margin-right

margin-left

Use

gap:20px;

Cleaner.

#6. object-fit
object-fit:cover;

Makes images/videos fill the box without distortion.

#7. border-radius

Rounds corners.

Example

border-radius:20px;
#8. box-shadow

Adds depth.

Example

box-shadow:0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.2);
